  "detailed_description": "Battle of the Boros is an action adventure RPG set during a mysterious invasion and occupation of New York City.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou play Kristen and the team of survivors she assembles to investigate what happened and reclaim the city.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nYou control a team of up to three characters at a time, each of who fights a little differently.  Some specialize in attack, some in defense and some in support.<br />\r\n<br />\r\nThrough camping and chatting with your teammates you form friendships and can become even stronger!",
